Sorry I did not think about this clearer. Now what I think is better is
```
interface HistogramCardFobData {
    scale: TemporalScale;
    steps: number[];
}

interface ScalarCardFobData {
    scale: Scale;
    minMax: [number, number];
}

type FobCardData =  HistogramCardFobData | ScalarCardFobData
```

